# .NET code quality

- Style source of truth is root `.editorconfig`; analyzers are enabled via `Directory.Build.props` (`EnableNETAnalyzers`, `EnforceCodeStyleInBuild`).
- Prefer file-scoped namespaces, `_camelCase` private fields, and `I`-prefixed interfaces.
- Before committing, ensure:

```bash
dotnet format AICommander.sln --verify-no-changes
dotnet build AICommander.sln
dotnet test AICommander.sln
```

- Local hooks (Husky.Net): pre-commit format verify, pre-push tests, commit-msg CommitLint.Net; do not skip them.
- Package versions are centralized in `Directory.Packages.props` — do not add `Version=` on `PackageReference` items.
- For Core/behavior changes, follow pragmatic TDD (`.cursor/rules/tdd.mdc`, [docs/testing.md](docs/testing.md)).
- Architecture rules and hotkey gotchas live in `.agents/AGENTS.md`.
